<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2020-04-08</DATELINE><TITLE>The Imperfect Cytokine Storm: Severe COVID-19 with ARDS in Patient on Durable LVAD Support</TITLE><BODY>Abstract As health systems worldwide grapple with the COVID-19 pandemic, patients on durable LVAD support represent a unique population at risk for the disease. We outline such a patient who developed COVID-19 complicated by “cytokine storm” with severe ARDS and myocardial injury; and describe the challenges that arose during management.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>